# 🚀 How to Run

## 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
  git clone https://github.com/your-username/cat-qubit-stabilization-dashboard.git
  cd cat-qubit-stabilization-dashboard 

## 2. Install Dependencies 
```bash
  pip install -r requirements.txt

## 3. Install Streamlit (if needed)
```bash
  pip install streamlit

## 4. Install ngrok
Download ngrok: 
https://ngrok.com/download 
Then authenticate your account
```bash
  ("ngrok config add-authtoken YOUR_TOKEN_HERE")

## 5. Run Application
```bash
  streamlit run app.py

## 6. (Optional) Share via ngrok
```bash
  ngrok http 8501
- This will generate a public URL for sharing your dashboard
  
